This is your daily digest for the voice <%= @voice.title %>.

<% if @contents.empty? %>
  There are no new contents today for the voice.
<% else %>
  These are the new contents added today to the voice:
  
  <% @contents.each do |content| %>
    - <%= content.class %>: <%= content.url %>
    <% unless content.description.blank? %>
      <%= content.description %>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
<% end %>

You can visit this voice to check out all contents from past days:
<%= voice_url(@voice) %>